<Docs title="Releases" description="Dep Beacon release and CI workflow.">
  <h1>Releases</h1>
  <p>
    Releases use Changesets for npm package versioning and GitHub Actions for validation, docs deployment, VSIX packaging, and marketplace publishing.
  </p>

  <h2>Local validation</h2>
  <pre><code>pnpm run validate</code></pre>

  <h2>Secrets</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>`NPM_TOKEN` publishes public npm packages with provenance.</li>
    <li>`VSCE_PAT` publishes the packaged VSIX to Visual Studio Marketplace.</li>
    <li>The Open VSX token publishes the same VSIX to Open VSX.</li>
    <li>`CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN` and `CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID` deploy docs to Cloudflare Pages.</li>
  </ul>
</Docs>
